Youths in Bulagu village, Budalang i sub-location, Bunyala subcounty, have been urged to register for ID cards. They can go to the registrar of persons office every Tuesday to apply, village elder Marcela Taabu said.She spoke on Saturday at the burial of Clementina Auma, mother of Cornell Okumu, the chairman of Budalang i MP Ababu Namwamba s advisory committee.